{"lemma": "سَرَفٌ", "slug": "سَرَفٌ", "root": "س.ر.ف", "root_slug": "س-ر-ف", "root_link": "/words/roots/س-ر-ف", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": false}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 1, "pos_tags": ["noun"], "has_etymology": false, "sense_count": 3}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n19598", "n19601", "n19602", "n19603"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "dissipation", "fa": "اسراف", "ur": "اسراف", "tr": "israf", "id": "pemborosan", "bn": "ইসরাফ", "es": "despilfarro", "fr": "dissipation", "de": "Verschwendung", "ru": "растрата", "zh": "浪费"}, "definition": {"source": "wiktextract", "senses": [{"pos": "noun", "gloss": "dissipation, waste"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "exaggeration, immoderateness, intemperance"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "extravagance, prodigality", "examples": [{"text": "وَلِمَ جَعَلُوا الْجُودَ سَرَفًا وَٱلْأَثْرَةَ جَهْلًا", "english": "Why do they portray benevolence as extravagance and depict unselfishness as folly?"}, {"text": "السرف: تجاوز الحد في كلِّ فعل يفعله الإنسان، وإن كان ذلك في الإنفاق أشهر"}]}]}, "etymology": null, "ipa": null, "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n19598", "headword_ar": "سَرِفَ", "root": "srf", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafN", "text_ar": "سَرَفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He was ignorant:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he was unmindful, negligent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "heedless."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) [In these senses it is trans.: you say,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarifahu", "text_ar": "سَرِفَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, M, K,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafN", "text_ar": "سَرَفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, * M, K, *)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He was unmindful, negligent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "heedless, of it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, K;) namely, a thing: (S, M:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he was ignorant of it:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he missed it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, * M, K; * [in the first and third of which, only the inf. n. of the verb in this sense in mentioned, and expl. as syn. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xaTaA^N", "text_ar": "خَطَاٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ";]) syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^axoTaA^ahu", "text_ar": "اَخْطَاَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (M.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Talabotuhumo fasarifotuhumo", "text_ar": "طَلَبْتُهُمْ فَسَرِفْتُهُمْ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I sought them and missed them:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "was ignorant of them."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarifa Alqawoma", "text_ar": "سَرِفَ القَوْمَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He passed by the people,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "party, and left them behind him."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M.) As relates, of an Arab of the desert, with whom some companions of his made an appointment to meet him in a certain place of the mosque, and to whom he broke his promise, that, being asked respecting that, he said,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mararotu bikumo fasarifotukumo", "text_ar": "مَرَرْتُ بِكُمْ فَسَرِفْتُكُمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I passed by you and"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I was unmindful of you."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) And hence the saying of Jereer, (S, TA,) praising the Benoo-Umeiyeh, (TA,)"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "A^aEoTawoA hunayodapa yaHoduwhaA vamaAniyapN\n                      \n                     \n                        maA fiY EaTaAy^ihimu min~N walaA sarafu"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They gave a hundred camels, eight"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "persons"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "driving them,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "urging them by singing to them: there was not in their gift reproach for a benefit conferred, nor"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "unmindfulness:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or the meaning is,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "nor missing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xaTaA^N", "text_ar": "خَطَاٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "); that is, they did not miss the proper place of the gift by their giving it to such as did not deserve it and refusing it to the deserving. (S, TA.) You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarifotu yamiynahu", "text_ar": "سَرِفْتُ يَمِينَهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I was unacquainted with,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "knew not, his oath."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b2-  ["}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafN", "text_ar": "سَرَفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is also, as expl. below,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "syn. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_isoraAfN", "text_ar": "اـِسْرَافٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", but as a subst., having no verb properly belonging to it.]       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafati Al$~ajarapa", "text_ar": "سَرَفَتِ الشَّجَرَةَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (ISk, S, K,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarofN", "text_ar": "سَرْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (ISk, S,) said of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "surofap", "text_ar": "سُرْفَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[q. v.],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It ate the leaves of the tree:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(ISk, S, K:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafati Alxa$aba", "text_ar": "سَرَفَتِ الخَشَبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is likewise said of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "surofap", "text_ar": "سُرْفَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it ate the wood"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (Z, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "surifati Al$~ajarapu", "text_ar": "سُرِفَتِ الشَّجَرَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (ISk, S, M, TA,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarofN", "text_ar": "سَرْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (ISk,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The tree had its leaves eaten by the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "surofap", "text_ar": "سُرْفَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "was smitten,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "lighted on, by the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "surofap", "text_ar": "سُرْفَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (ISk, M, TA:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarifa Alxa$abu", "text_ar": "سَرِفَ الخَشَبُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the wood was eaten by the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "surofap", "text_ar": "سُرْفَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], the verb in this phrase being quasi-pass. of the verb in the phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafati Als~urofapu Alxa$ab~", "text_ar": "سَرَفَتِ السُّرْفَةُ الخَشَبّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", like as"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaTima", "text_ar": "حَطِمَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 1351}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaEiqa", "text_ar": "صَعِقَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "are quasi-passives of the verbs in the phrases"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaTamatohu Als~in~u", "text_ar": "حَطَمَتْهُ السِّنُّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaEaqatohu Als~amaA='u", "text_ar": "صَعَقَتْهُ السَّمَا=ءُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Z, TA:) and [hence] one says also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarifa AlT~aEaAmu", "text_ar": "سَرِفَ الطَّعَامُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The wheat,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "food, was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, cankered,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "eaten away;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as though smitten, or lighted on, by the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "surofap", "text_ar": "سُرْفَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (M, TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence also,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "surifato A^u*unu Al$~aApi", "text_ar": "سُرِفَتْ اُذُنُ الشَّاةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ear of the sheep,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "goat, was entirely cut off."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafato waladahaA", "text_ar": "سَرَفَتْ وَلَدَهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "She"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a mother)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "injured her child by"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "too"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "much milk."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, K, * TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "M", "K", "TA", "ISk", "Z"]}, {"entry_id": "n19601", "headword_ar": "سَرَفْ", "root": "srf", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "inf. n. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarifa", "text_ar": "سَرِفَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[q. v.]. (S, * M, Msb, K. *) ―         -b2-  And also a subst. from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asorafa", "text_ar": "اَسْرَفَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (Msb;) i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_isoraAfN", "text_ar": "اـِسْرَافٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (M;) signifying"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Excess,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "transgression, of the just,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "right, bound,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "limit,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "measure; extravagant, exorbitant,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "immoderate, action"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "conduct;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, Msb, TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contr. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qaSodN", "text_ar": "قَصْدٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, K.) See also 4, in two places. ―         -b3-  [Hence,] (tropical:)  The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "overflowing of water from the sides"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a watering-trough, or tank; as in the  saying,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "*ahaba maA='u AlHawoDi sarafFA", "text_ar": "ذَهَبَ مَا=ءُ الحَوْضِ سَرَفًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The water of the watering-trough,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "tank,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "went away running to waste,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "overflowed from its sides:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafu AlmaA='i", "text_ar": "سَرَفُ المَا=ءِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what goes, of water, without irrigating and without profit:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or rather"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "its going for nought:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] you say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^arowati Albiy^oru Aln~axiyla", "text_ar": "اَرْوَتِ البِيْرُ النَّخِيلَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wa*ahaba baqiy~apu AlmaA='i sarafFA", "text_ar": "وَذَهَبَ بَقِيَّةُ المَا=ءِ سَرَفًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The well irrigated the palmtrees, and the rest of the water went for nought, in waste"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (Sh, TA.) ―         -b4-  And"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Addictedness"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "DaraAwapN", "text_ar": "ضَرَاوَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", S, K, or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lahajN", "text_ar": "لَهَجٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "M) to a thing, (M,) or in respect of wine. (K, TA.) It is said in a trad. (S, M) of 'Áïsheh, (TA,)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_in~a lil~aHomi sarafFA kasarafi", "text_ar": "اـِنَّ لِلَّحْمِ سَرَفًا كَسَرَفِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alxamori", "text_ar": "الخَمْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Verily there is an addictedness to flesh-meat like the addictedness to wine"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (S, M, TA:) i. e. he who is accustomed to it is addicted to the eating thereof, like as he who is constantly drinking wine is addicted thereto, having little selfrestraint therefrom: or the meaning here is"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "unmindfulness"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of consequences with respect to flesh-meat"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]: or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "corruptness of conduct, arising from hardness of heart, and daringness to disobey, and self-impulsion to the gratification of appetite:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) or it may be [that the meaning is,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "there is an extravagance with respect to flesh-meat"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,] from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlA_isoraAfu", "text_ar": "الاـِسْرَافُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, TA) in expenditure for that which is not needed, or otherwise than in obedience [to the law of God]. (TA.) ―         -b5-  It is also said in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laA yanotahibu Alr~ajulu nuhobapF *aAta", "text_ar": "لَا يَنْتَهِبُ الرَّجُلُ نُهْبَةً ذَاتَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafK wahuwa muw^ominN", "text_ar": "سَرَفٍ وَهُوَ مُوْمِنٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "*aAta $arafK waqadorK kabiyrK", "text_ar": "ذَاتَ شَرَفٍ وَقَدْرٍ كَبِيرٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The man shall not take a thing as spoil that is of high and great estimation, he being a believer"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (K, TA:) [for] people disapprove of that: (TA:) and it is also related with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$", "text_ar": "ش"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "*At $arafK", "text_ar": "ذات شَرَفٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (K.)"}], "source_refs": ["K", "TA", "M", "S"]}, {"entry_id": "n19602", "headword_ar": "سَرِفٌ", "root": "srf", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Ignorant;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IAar, M, Msb, TA;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "musorifN", "text_ar": "مُسْرِفٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (IAar, TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "unmindful, negligent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "heedless."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rajulN sarifN Alfuw^aAdi", "text_ar": "رَجُلٌ سَرِفٌ الفُوَادِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A man missing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mistaking, in heart,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mind; negligent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "heedless, therein."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rajulN sarifu AlEaqoli", "text_ar": "رَجُلٌ سَرِفُ العَقْلِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A man having little intellect,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "intelligence:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "corrupt in intellect;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "accord. to Z, from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarafati Als~urofapu Alxa$aba", "text_ar": "سَرَفَتِ السُّرْفَةُ الخَشَبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", of which the quasipass. is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarifa", "text_ar": "سَرِفَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[q. v.; meaning that it is from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarifN", "text_ar": "سَرِفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as a part. n. of this latter verb]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aroDN sarifapN", "text_ar": "اَرْضٌ سَرِفَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, M, K,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waAdK sarifN", "text_ar": "وَادٍ سَرِفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A land, and a valley, abounding with the"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "worm,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "caterpillar,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "small creeping thing, called"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "surofap", "text_ar": "سُرْفَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, M, * K, TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["IAar", "TA", "S", "M", "K"]}, {"entry_id": "n19603", "headword_ar": "سُرُفٌ", "root": "srf", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A certain white thing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "substance"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "resembling the web of the silkworm."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ibn-'Abbád, O, K.)"}], "so